title: Bryn Mawr Rehab Hospital Hosts First Swing Golf Clinic: 15 participated in the hands-on clinic ...
text: ( Source : MLH - Main Line Health Inc) On Wednesday, September 30 , 2015 , Bryn Mawr Rehabilitation Hospital hosted the 2015 First Swing Golf Clinic in partnership with the Eastern Amputee Golf Association (EAGA) and RiverCrest Golf Club
